dct_description_sm: author Iohannes Mejerus. Hus. Regæ. Majis. Mathematicq.
Latitudinal and longitudinal lines along margins.
Shows topography, vegetation, waterways, shoals, routes.
Pictorial vignettes of flora, fauna, windmills, boat, sea monster.
2 inset maps: Grundtriß von Fridrichstadt, anno 1649 ; Grundtriß der stadt Eckernföerde.
This copy has pencil inscription in lower left: 241.
